creator: Jane Hunter
descriptionHtml: A central hub that connects Solo Parents around the globe and allow access to all the support and encouragement we offer—in one place—24/7. Keep in touch with solo parents on a consistent basis through the notifications functions as well as create a forum for all parents to keep in touch with one another.
descriptionShort: Connecting Solo Parents to support and encouragement 24/7

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We're always adding new features and fixing bugs!

What's new
- Messaging (new): You can now copy and paste message text. Channel owners can now edit or delete a channel.

Bug fixes
- Lists: Fixed carousel bug where items would advance incorrectly
- Messaging: We fixed a bug where the app would close after the device was locked for an extended period of time.
- Events: We resolved timezone display issues

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel
- Administers can set channels to be public for anyone to join

Fixed:
- Media playback now stops when you force close the app
- Fixed a Messaging issue causing link previews to cause the channel to crash
